  ('color-call-tennis-ball-catch-on-single-leg-balance', 'Start with slower cue timing, shorter distances, and lower balance demand. Require clean catches and safe stops before adding chaos.', 'No default gender-based adjustment. Scale by training age, vision/vestibular status, joint history, pregnancy/postpartum symptoms, fatigue state, sport demand, and demonstrated coordination quality.'),
